OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,FOver 400,000 KitKats have been stolen
OL,7,Ffrom a truck in Switzerland, which
OL,8,Fcould cause a shortage of the bars
OL,9,Fahead of Easter, Nestle has said.
OL,11,FThe food giant said the vast quantity
OL,12,Fof chocolate disappeared last week
OL,13,Fwhile being transported between Italy
OL,14,Fand Poland.
OL,16,F"We've always encouraged people to
OL,17,Fhave a break with KITKAT - but it
OL,18,Fseems thieves have
