OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,Ftaken the message too literally and
OL,7,Fmade a break with more than 12 tonnes
OL,8,Fof our chocolate," a KitKat
OL,9,Fspokesperson said on Thursday.
