OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,F"Whilst we appreciate the criminals'
OL,7,Fexceptional taste, the fact remains
OL,8,Fthat cargo theft is an escalating
OL,9,Fissue for businesses of all sizes.
OL,10,FWith more sophisticated schemes being
OL,11,Fdeployed on a regular basis, we have
OL,12,Fchosen to go public with our own
OL,13,Fexperience in the hope that it raises
OL,14,Fawareness of an increasingly common
OL,15,Fcriminal trend."
