PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774865180
OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,FNestle warned the theft "may lead to a
OL,7,Fshortage of KITKATs appearing on
OL,8,Fshelf, which is why consumers,
OL,9,Funfortunately, may struggle to find
OL,10,Ftheir favourite chocolates ahead of
OL,11,FEaster".
OL,13,FThe location of the bars and the
OL,14,Fvehicle, and the identity of the
OL,15,Fthief, remain unaccounted for.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
