OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1774865180
OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,FKitKat has said it believes the
OL,7,Fmissing units could enter unofficial
OL,8,Fsales channels across Europe, and if
OL,9,Fso, the products would be able to be
OL,10,Ftraced thanks to their unique batch
OL,11,Fcodes.
OL,13,F"If a match is found, the scanner will
OL,14,Fbe given clear instructions on how to
OL,15,Falert KITKAT who will then share the
OL,16,Fevidence appropriately," Nestle said.
