OL,3,COver 400,000 KitKats stolen from a
OL,4,Ctruck in Switzerland
OL,6,FThe theft comes after a joint report
OL,7,Ffrom the International Union of Marine
OL,8,FInsurance and the Transported Asset
OL,9,FProtection Association EMEA, which
OL,10,Foutlined a rise in cargo theft and
OL,11,Ffreight fraud, with more sophisticated
OL,12,Fmethods of deception and apprehension
OL,13,Fbecoming increasingly common.
